  <brief_title>A Multi-Center Study on the Utility of Non-invasive Carboxyhemoglobin and Total Hemoglobin Measurement in Emergency Department Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center Study on the Utility of Non-invasive Carboxyhemoglobin and Total Hemoglobin Measurement in Emergency Department Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
